title: Chicago's Large Lot Program sowing change in inner-city communities

title_detail.value: Chicago's Large Lot Program sowing change in inner-city communities

summary: Chicago's Large Lot Program is promoting positive change in inner-city neighborhoods by enabling residents to buy and repurpose vacant lots that currently attracted crime and other problems.
